text:
seeing an issue with if/else statements - if i try to render modules within those blocks, it makes it so no modules are editable on the page level. simple test case: ```{% if true %}
      &lt;p&gt;IF STATEMENT&lt;/p&gt;
        {% text %}
      {% else %}
            &lt;p&gt;ELSE STATEMENT&lt;/p&gt;
        {% image %}
      {% endif %}``` when you get to the page editor, the sidebar just says “Body Modules” and there is no way to edit anything
